NAME
	query_thousands_separator - lpc extension

SYNOPSIS
	string query_thousands_separator(string locale)

DESCRIPTION
	This command works with the LPC_EXT_QUERY_LOCALE_DATA extension.
	If the extension is not enabled the function returns ",".

	You can find the extension on github here:
	https://github.com/november-kilo/dgd-lpc-ext

RETURN VALUE
	Returns a string that contains the seperator for numbers based on
	locale.

EXAMPLES
	string st;

	st = query_thousands_separator("US");

SEE ALSO
	afun/blog_it, afun/filelastmod, afun/files_modified,
	afun/sqlite3_exec, afun/sqlite3_select, afun/query_locale_data
